item.title: Prayer bpn12413 in Namibia
item.description: Pa kara Mutunditipo wamaudito hanashi Ove ndi? Ghamba: Mfumwa kwaKarunga! Ghuye ndje Karunga! Navantje vapikwendi nka navantje kwa kara mudimuragho dendi! (Source category: Rugciriku : LIVATERO) (Bahaiprayers.net ID: 12413)
